---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import { Check } from "lucide-react";
---
<Layout title="About Invisible Text" description="Learn more about Invisible Text, our mission, values, and the team behind the tools.">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-black tracking-tight mb-8 text-center">
        About Invisible Text
        <div class="h-2 w-24 bg-emerald-400 mx-auto mt-4"></div>
      </h1>

      <div class="space-y-16">
        <section class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border-2 border-black shadow-lg">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-lg">
            Our mission at Invisible Text is to empower creators, marketers, and developers with tools that are simple, effective, and privacy-focused. We aim to remove friction from content generation and manipulation, offering solutions that help you move faster and smarter online.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border-2 border-black shadow-lg">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Story</h2>
          <p class="text-lg">
            Invisible Text began as a side project aimed at solving small everyday content and formatting frustrations. What started with a few basic utilities has evolved into a platform offering a wide range of tools for invisible text generation, Unicode formatting, and productivity-enhancing features. Today, we're trusted by users worldwide to provide lightweight, no-nonsense tools they can rely on.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border-2 border-black shadow-lg">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Meet the Team</h2>
          <p class="text-lg">
            We're a small, passionate team of developers, designers, and problem-solvers who believe in building with clarity and purpose. We work remotely across different time zones, collaborating asynchronously to create tools that just work.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border-2 border-black shadow-lg">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Our Values</h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <Check className="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-600" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Simplicity</h3>
                <p>We believe the best tools are the ones you don’t have to think about. Clear, minimal interfaces are our priority.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <Check className="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-600" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Privacy</h3>
                <p>Your data is yours. We don’t track you, and we don’t store your content—ever.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <Check className="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-600" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Speed</h3>
                <p>Every feature is designed to get out of your way—fast loading, lightweight pages, and instant feedback.</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <Check className="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-600" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Accessibility</h3>
                <p>We design with accessibility in mind so everyone can benefit from our tools, regardless of device or ability.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border-2 border-black shadow-lg">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Looking Ahead</h2>
          <p class="text-lg">
            We're continuously exploring new ways to support creators and developers. From enhanced formatting utilities to AI-powered content tools, the future of Invisible Text will be shaped by feedback from our users—and the ever-evolving challenges of digital work.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl border-2 border-black shadow-lg text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Get in Touch</h2>
          <p class="text-lg mb-8">
            Have feedback, questions, or collaboration ideas? We’d love to hear from you. Reach out and help shape the future of Invisible Text.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-block bg-black hover:bg-gray-800 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg transition-colors"
          >
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
